data.description: Welcome home to this stunning like-new home in the coveted Creekside Ridge neighborhood. You are greeted with beautiful ceramic wood plank looking tile flooring upon entry and will also notice a spacious dining room. Take a walk through the breezeway you will find the spacious open kitchen and family room. The kitchen has granite counter-tops, an island with a breakfast bar, a smooth cook-top, and plenty of cabinets and counter space for your inner chef. In the family room, you will enjoy the cozy fireplace in a space made to both entertain and relax. The beautifully upgraded iron railing on the curved staircase gives the home a custom regal feel. The master suite is conveniently located downstairs with a full on-suite bathroom, double vanities, separate shower, and tub and a large walk-in closet. Upstairs features a loft and spacious secondary bedrooms. The back yard back has lots of privacy as the home backs up to an easement. You'll enjoy a covered patio and lots of space to play, BBQ, and entertain. Don't miss the chance to call this house your home today!
